<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="About UNI-SERVICES — our vision, mission, values, and the people building the future of digital services." />
  <title>About Us | UNI-SERVICES</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'><text y='.9em' font-size='90'>⬡</text></svg>" />
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ===================== PAGE LOADER ===================== -->
  <div id="page-loader">
    <div class="loader-inner">
      <div class="loader-logo">UNI-SERVICES</div>
      <div class="loader-bar"><div class="loader-bar-fill"></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- BG Orbs -->
  <div class="bg-orbs" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
    <div class="orb orb-2"></div>
    <div class="orb orb-3"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- ===================== NAVBAR ========================= -->
  <!--  navbar.ejs   -->
    <%- include('navbar') %>

  <div class="nav-mobile">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <a href="/about">About</a>
    <a href="/contact" class="nav-cta">Get in Touch</a>  </div>

  <main>

    <!-- ==================== PAGE HERO ==================== -->
    <section class="page-hero section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-tag reveal">Our Story</div>
        <h1 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1" style="font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4.2rem); text-align:center; max-width:700px; margin:0 auto 1rem;">
          We're Building the<br /><span class="gradient-text" style="background:var(--gradient-hero);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;">Future of Digital Life</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="section-subtitle reveal reveal-delay-2" style="text-align:center;margin:0 auto;">
          UNI-SERVICES was born from a simple frustration: why should accessing great healthcare, entertainment, and storage require five different apps, five passwords, and five monthly fees?
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ==================== VISION & MISSION ============= -->
    <section class="section" style="padding-top:0;">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-grid">

          <div class="about-block reveal">
            <div class="about-block-icon">🔭</div>
            <h3>Our Vision</h3>
            <p>
              A world where every person — regardless of geography or income — has frictionless access to world-class healthcare, entertainment, and secure digital infrastructure through one beautifully simple platform.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
              We envision UNI-SERVICES becoming the operating system of everyday digital life: the single trusted layer between people and the services that matter most.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="about-block reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <div class="about-block-icon">🎯</div>
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>
              To eliminate digital fragmentation by building deeply integrated, privacy-first services that respect users' time, data, and intelligence.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
              We design every product with one principle: <em style="color:var(--accent-cyan);">make the complex feel effortless.</em> From booking a doctor to booking a movie seat to storing a file — everything should feel like second nature.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="about-block reveal">
            <div class="about-block-icon">🧭</div>
            <h3>Our Approach</h3>
            <p>
              We build iteratively, listen obsessively, and move with speed without sacrificing craft. Every pixel, every API response, and every support interaction is treated as a product decision.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="about-block reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <div class="about-block-icon">🌍</div>
            <h3>Our Impact</h3>
            <p>
              Serving users across 40+ cities, we've enabled 120,000+ doctor consultations, sold 800,000+ event tickets, and securely store over 5 petabytes of personal and enterprise data.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div><!-- /about-grid -->

        <!-- ==================== FOUNDER ================== -->
        <div class="founder-section reveal">

  <div class="founder-avatar-wrap">
    <div class="founder-avatar">
      <img src="images/ayush-srivastava.jpeg" alt="Ayush Srivastava" />
    </div>
    <div class="founder-badge">Founder</div>
  </div>

  <div class="founder-content">
    <div class="founder-tag">A Word From the Founder</div>

    <div class="founder-name">
      Ayush Srivastava
    <span class="founder-verified" aria-label="Verified">✓</span>
    </div>

    <div class="founder-role">
      Founder & CEO | UNI-SERVICES
    </div>

    <p class="founder-quote">
      "When we started UNI-SERVICES, the motivation was clear: everyday life was being fragmented across too many apps. Simple tasks — booking an appointment, saving a document, planning an evening — felt unnecessarily complicated. We believed technology should do the opposite: it should simplify, unify, and make life easier.
UNI-SERVICES isn’t just a product; it’s a philosophy. Our guiding principle is simple — if a feature makes someone’s day better, we build it. If it doesn’t, we leave it out. That discipline keeps us focused on what truly matters: creating digital experiences that reduce friction and bring clarity.
As a founder, my vision is not to overwhelm users with options, but to give them one seamless platform that feels natural, intuitive, and genuinely helpful. That’s the promise of UNI-SERVICES, and it’s the standard we hold ourselves to every day."

    </p>

    <div class="founder-signature">
      — Ayush
    </div>

  </div>

  

</div><!-- /founder-section -->

<!-- ==================== CO-FOUNDER ================== -->
        <div class="founder-section founder-section-reverse reveal">

          <div class="founder-content">
            <div class="founder-tag">A Word From the Co-Founder</div>

            <div class="founder-name">
              Vishal Yadav
              <span class="founder-verified">✓</span>
            </div>

            <div class="founder-role">
              Co-Founder & COO | UNI-SERVICES
            </div>

            <p class="founder-quote">
              "I didn’t start UNI-SERVICES because apps were failing — I started it because they were disconnected. Healthcare, entertainment, and storage all evolved independently, but real life doesn’t operate in silos.

UNI-SERVICES is built on a simple belief: essential digital services should feel connected, not scattered. Our goal isn’t to add more apps to your life — it’s to simplify how they work together.

We design with intention, build with clarity, and focus only on what genuinely adds value."
            </p>

            <div class="founder-signature">
              — Vishal
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="founder-avatar-wrap">
            <div class="founder-avatar">
              <img src="" alt="Vishal Yadav" />
            </div>
            <div class="founder-badge">Co-Founder</div>
          </div>

        </div>
        <!-- /co-founder-section -->

        <!-- ==================== VALUES ================== -->
        <div>
          <div class="section-tag reveal" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Our Values</div>
          <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1" style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">The Principles We Live By</h2>

          <div class="values-grid">
            <div class="value-card reveal">
              <div class="value-num">01</div>
              <h4>User Obsession</h4>
              <p>Every decision starts and ends with the user. We track satisfaction metrics daily and treat every complaint as a gift.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
              <div class="value-num">02</div>
              <h4>Privacy by Default</h4>
              <p>We don't sell data. We don't show ads. We make money only when users find genuine value in our services.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
              <div class="value-num">03</div>
              <h4>Craft Over Speed</h4>
              <p>We'd rather ship something exceptional slowly than something mediocre fast. Quality is non-negotiable.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value-card reveal">
              <div class="value-num">04</div>
              <h4>Radical Transparency</h4>
              <p>We publish our uptime, our pricing, our data practices — openly. No dark patterns, no fine print traps.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
              <div class="value-num">05</div>
              <h4>Inclusive Design</h4>
              <p>Our products are built for everyone — across ages, abilities, devices, and connectivity conditions.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
              <div class="value-num">06</div>
              <h4>Long-Term Thinking</h4>
              <p>We optimize for a 10-year relationship with our users, not a 10-week growth chart. Loyalty is earned, not hacked.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!-- /values -->

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ==================== CTA ========================== -->
    <section class="cta-section section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-box reveal">
          <div class="section-tag">Join Us</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Become Part of the Story</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">
            We're growing — and we'd love for you to experience what we're building. Start exploring for free.
          </p>
          <div class="cta-actions">
            <a href="/#services" class="btn btn-primary">
              Explore Services
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-ghost">Talk to Us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <!-- ===================== FOOTER ========================= -->
   <!-- inclue footer.ejs -->
  <%- include('footer') %>

  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>